description.en:
ACENT transcends the blockchain paradigm, further improves internet infrastructure and makes steps ahead to solve scalability problem by integrating blockchain into decentralized web browser.
Therefore, I am confident that ACENT will become an universal and well-accepted technology. We uphold Satoshi Nakamoto's spirit to provide blockchain technology to masses.
